author: Master Student Ahmed R. Abd .Shaheen,Prof. Dr. Laheeb M. I. Alzubaidy  University of Mosul-College of Computer Sciences & Math – Software  Dept

comments.undefined: This ontology aims to describe factors affecting of Global Virtual Teams (GVTs)Performance in Global Software Development(GSD) through the use of a set of concepts and the relationships that link them and the characteristics that represent the features of each concept and the restrictions imposed on these characteristics, where ontology with class instances forms a knowledge base that helps in obtaining a broader understanding of factors affecting GSD.
